document_data.Inhabitants:
[[File:Korinn Archipelago shipwreck.png|thumb|''Survivors of a slave shipwreck on the shores of the [[Island of Viledel]].''|335x335px]]
The inhabitants of these islands were primarily made up of Northmen, Some remnants of the [[Ffolk]] were also known to inhabit the isles.

The [[white dragon]] [[Arveiaturace]] was known to sometimes hunt in the archipelago.{{Cite dragon/231/Wyrms of the North: Arveiaturace|36}}
